{
  "id": 4790543041298432,
  "name": "Declarative Shadow DOM 'shadowrootadoptedstylesheets'",
  "summary": "Allows for Declarative Shadow DOM (DSD) to specify adopted stylesheets at parse time. 'shadowrootadoptedstylesheets' supports a space-separated list of specifiers that each get fetched (exactly like a JavaScript import) and added to 'adoptedStyleSheets' in specified order. Developers are encouraged to preload the stylesheets referenced via <link rel=\"modulepreload\" as=\"style\"> in the head to prevent late fetches.",
